## 4. Non-Functional Requirements

### 4.1 Performance
- Page load time < 3s on 3G connection
- Form submission < 2s with stable internet
- Offline features available within 1s

### 4.2 Security
- All data encrypted in transit (TLS 1.3+) and at rest (AES-256)
- No persistent cookies or trackers
- Regular security audits (OWASP Top 10 compliance)

### 4.3 Usability
- WCAG 2.1 AA compliant (contrast, keyboard nav, screen reader support)
- Literacy-friendly: icons + audio support for low-literacy users
- Language switcher always visible

### 4.4 Reliability
- 99% uptime for core services
- Auto-save drafts every 30 seconds
- Graceful degradation during network loss

### 4.5 Maintainability
- Modular codebase (Next.js + REST API)
- Comprehensive logging (anonymized)
- Easy to add new languages or regions

