## 6. System Architecture (High-Level)
[User Browser]  
       ↓ (HTTPS)  
[Next.js Frontend (Vercel)]  
       ↓ (API Calls)  
[Node.js/Django Backend (Render)]  
       ↓  
[PostgreSQL Database]  
       ↓  
[Cloud Storage (for uploads)]  
       ↓  
[Optional: SMS Gateway, Jitsi, OpenStreetMap]

- Frontend: Next.js (PWA, SSR, i18n)
- Backend: RESTful API with role-based access control
- Database: PostgreSQL with encrypted fields
- Auth: Firebase Auth (optional)
- Offline: Workbox service workers

